data.description: Discover the perfect blend of tranquility and accessibility in this charming 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home nestled on 3 acres of picturesque countryside. Boasting a thoughtfully designed split floor plan, this residence offers both privacy and functionality. Immerse yourself in the beauty of the surrounding nature while enjoying the convenience of being just a short distance from town. This property invites you to embrace a lifestyle that combines the serenity of rural living with the amenities of urban proximity. Call today schedule showing!
